      "date": "2019-10-22 18:35:12.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nDoes a similar issue exist for routed sends? How do we ensure that a router forwards to/from a consistent interface?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "8e87a8580b924c347f8f8f6097fd68fbb931d1f5",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 683,
        "name": "jenkins",
