      },
      "date": "2019-10-22 18:56:16.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nBuild Successful \n\nhttps://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews-patchless/9387/ : SUCCESS\n\nhttps://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/69177/ : SUCCESS",
